{"tid":1811452,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"學術性討論各種示威策略的成效","createTime":"2020-01-04T16:52:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T03:10:26.000Z","uid":319295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2b362a345e8924ac127054f42d59092ebf4b94b2","tid":1811452,"uid":319295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:52:55.000Z","msg":"先看：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/future/article/20190513-it-only-takes-35-of-people-to-change-the-world\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Ffuture%2Farticle%2F20190513-it-only-takes-35-of-people-to-change-the-world&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLUcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=6c21015c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Ffuture%2Farticle%2F20190513-it-only-takes-35-of-people-to-change-the-world&h=d728662f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/future/article/20190513-it-only-takes-35-of-people-to-change-the-world</a><br />\n<br />\n可用於送中的論點：<br />\n參加度遠遠超過3.5%，贏面應該大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（但中共是納稅黨以外史無前例的對手）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港算是和勇不分的先例，但國際戰上勇武容易讓外國割。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三罷是最有力的春袋。<br />\n黃色經濟圈（罷賣）在南非推倒apartheid非常見效。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人認為和理非是唯一能持久的抗爭方法，勇武一旦淪為恐怖主義就注定失敗（所以暫時都還好）。在這戰，勇武是推動和理非遠遠超過3.5%的原因。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遊行能集氣和量度整體支持度，但是對大部分人來說時間成本大，只能幾個星期做一次。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈最為重要，原因是參加門欄低，能容易每天參與，而且每次懲罰或罷賣都有實體的功效，容易拉攏新的和理非積極參加。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人是感情動物，一旦開始了習慣罷賣，就等同於投資了精神時間去支持這場運動，就越想贏，就越繼續罷賣。現在要做的，就是一定要降低參加黃色經濟圈的門欄（商家容易加入，市民有清晰的指引，儘快劃分所有產品分類）。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90fe9693b4b295f8bf693bdf4627698bad2a9ab6","tid":1811452,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:53:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b8a2d7622fb61052425fb5fdaff72b78e33aaa2","tid":1811452,"uid":319295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b362a345e8924ac127054f42d59092ebf4b94b2","tid":1811452,"uid":319295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:52:55.000Z","msg":"先看：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/future/article/20190513-it-only-takes-35-of-people-to-change-the-world\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Ffuture%2Farticle%2F20190513-it-only-takes-35-of-people-to-change-the-world&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLUcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=6c21015c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Ffuture%2Farticle%2F20190513-it-only-takes-35-of-people-to-change-the-world&h=d728662f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/future/article/20190513-it-only-takes-35-of-people-to-change-the-world</a><br />\n<br />\n可用於送中的論點：<br />\n參加度遠遠超過3.5%，贏面應該大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（但中共是納稅黨以外史無前例的對手）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港算是和勇不分的先例，但國際戰上勇武容易讓外國割。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三罷是最有力的春袋。<br />\n黃色經濟圈（罷賣）在南非推倒apartheid非常見效。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人認為和理非是唯一能持久的抗爭方法，勇武一旦淪為恐怖主義就注定失敗（所以暫時都還好）。在這戰，勇武是推動和理非遠遠超過3.5%的原因。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遊行能集氣和量度整體支持度，但是對大部分人來說時間成本大，只能幾個星期做一次。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈最為重要，原因是參加門欄低，能容易每天參與，而且每次懲罰或罷賣都有實體的功效，容易拉攏新的和理非積極參加。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人是感情動物，一旦開始了習慣罷賣，就等同於投資了精神時間去支持這場運動，就越想贏，就越繼續罷賣。現在要做的，就是一定要降低參加黃色經濟圈的門欄（商家容易加入，市民有清晰的指引，儘快劃分所有產品分類）。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:57:41.000Z","msg":"應